<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_328_r1l3"><expan>Wırdıg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> doctor / der eren vnd <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> dıe <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l4">der <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gotſgab ʒu Bachrach <expan>ʒugang<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt ſeyn wır fro vnd <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l5"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd daʒ Jr ʒu <expan>gröſſer<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> möchtet / <expan>VVölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wo das an vns gelanget <expan>williklıch<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu tun / vvıe wol wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l7">doch eẅr <expan>p<ex>er</ex>ſon</expan> vnd gegenwertıkeıt . ſo eẅch das an <expan>gröſſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> nucʒe niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l8"><expan>gehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hett / <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> lıebſt bey vns geſehen <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> / Vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l9">notdurft vorʒuſein als Jr vormals freẅntlıch getan habt . Des wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l10"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd ein gancʒ <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> haben wellen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l11">wo Jr vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hınfür . <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> lıeb vnd <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> . <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
