<ab facs="#facs_328_r1l16"><expan>kottemp<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>weyhennecht<ex>en</ex></expan> gütlıch <expan>vollg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd becʒaln in maſſ </ab>
